Fourth Department,

August, 1983

(August 23, 1983) In the Matter of Martha W. Bennett, Appellant, v Perry Chambers et al., Constituting the Board of Elections of the County of Niagara, et al., *1014Respondents.

— Order unanimously affirmed, without costs. (See Matter of Ferris v Sadowski, 45 NY2d 815.) (Appeal from order of Niagara Supreme Court, Broughton, J. — Election Law.) Present — Doerr, J. P., Denman, Boomer, Green and Schnepp, JJ.
